Scripts taken and modified from bookcorpus repo

tokenize_sentlines.py is derived from https://github.com/soskek/bookcorpus
make_sentlines.py is derived and modified from https://github.com/soskek/bookcorpus

In order to aggregate 20_newsgroup dataset, use this command:

python scripts/make_sentlines.py data/20_newsgroup/ | python scripts/tokenize_sentlines.py  > all.txt
